metadata.user_intent:
Optimize for thermal management andOptimize the design for:
1. Signal integrity (40%)
2. Thermal management (30%)
3. Manufacturability (20%)
4. Cost (10%)

Constraints:
- Maintain minimum 0.5mm clearance
- High-current traces >1.5mm width
- Keep analog and digital sections isolated
- Separate power and communication planes

Goals:
- Achieve reliable multi-domain operation
- Maintain short critical signal paths
- Minimize EMI between power and communication sections
- Ensure even thermal distribution across the board signal integrity
